179
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:19,370
Mimi?

180
00:07:19,970 --> 00:07:20,570
Tentermon!

181
00:07:20,730 --> 00:07:21,730
And Izzy!

182
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:22,810
Hey!

183
00:07:23,790 --> 00:07:24,790
Hi, Mimi.

184
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,530
