230
00:09:00,770 --> 00:09:04,290
I haven't had anything to eat and my feet
are killing me in a giant limit custard

231
00:09:04,291 --> 00:09:06,670
trying to kiss me and all I want to do is
get out of here!

232
00:09:06,690 --> 00:09:07,410
