255
00:09:51,130 --> 00:09:51,570
Mimi!

256
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:52,810
Mimi, are you alright?

257
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:54,570
I'm not a bad person.

258
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:57,330
