here!

262
00:10:02,010 --> 00:10:03,910
All I want to do is get back home!

263
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:04,870
That's all!

264
00:10:05,130 --> 00:10:05,790
Please wait!

265
00:10:05,810 --> 00:10:07,750
I really think we ought to find our way
back!

266
00:10:08,050 --> 00:10:09,250
